{"tid":1524759,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城online] 要報仇先由檢討入手","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T18:20:56.000Z","uid":313697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac02043502da94d5d9ee9417be8a366ed9cbeadb","tid":1524759,"uid":313697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"[第一次開post請見諒]今天，相信不論是fa、前線、和理非，還是擁有良知的你也好，都十分傷心氣憤， 而且更想向popo報復， 但希望在這之前能聽一聽小弟一話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先，希望中後排的手足不要成為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">驚弓之鳥</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一聽到後退就馬上逃跑。反之， 當前線指示<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望撤退時就應該馬上撤退</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 不要使自己成為黑警的獵物。因此要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時時刻刻留意周圍情況</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n其次，希望大家能真正做到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">齊上齊落</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">別讓手足落單</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。相反，若我們<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人多勢眾而且齊心</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 我們才會有反擊的優勢。<br />\n<br />\n最後，到了裝備的問題，各系列的魔法師請繼續升級魔法。請容許小弟在此介紹一款與警棍無差的日用品：<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">實心擀麵棍</span></span></div><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n質量和長度也相約，只需少量改裝，即可成優質的近戰武器，各位手足更能自行開發科技樹，提高打小兵的威力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後的最後， 魔王一方已不再存有任何的道德底線，公然在交通工具毆打大量途人、手足，懇請各位再三思檢討一下自己的道德底線。 至於臥底的問題還請交由前線決定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰，但要檢討</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不流血、不受傷、不被捕，但要反擊</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">寧作飛灰不作浮塵</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"5b578d79b6bf02e26768f180d511b089a49cf480","tid":1524759,"uid":313697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:11:11.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"dd8d5c135416cf5ee240867d51ddbb4e67aa26f4","tid":1524759,"uid":313697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:13:19.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"abe8e929fb5e00b5be143fbc1348410950ef618a","tid":1524759,"uid":313697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:15:11.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"459aee95a0cad9943ac56fdccb28b87c844d420a","tid":1524759,"uid":313697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:20:56.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"}]}